title: Tell Me Why (Taylor's Version)
description:
This song is so catchy and fun, but what's the true story behind it? Amy, Ana, Lacey and Nick dissect and discuss.. and someone figures out a creative way to use this song in inconvenient situations!
Plus, we open up our very first fan mail! Thank you so much for all the Swift swag, Mike! WE LOVE IT! Thank you for making us feel special!
What does this song do for you? Is there anything that we missed? Hit us up!
